Description:
The warehouse, kitchen, infirmary, and archives are within your reach. 

They’re probably not as well-stocked as they were when the pirates lived here, but there should still be something useful. 

It looks like the pirates abandoned this area last, as the kitchen, infirmary, and archives are open and show signs of use. Only the warehouse door is closed.

The navy troops are already in the fortress, so you may only have time to investigate one of these rooms before they claim it for the admiralty.
DescriptionAction: Which room would you like to check?
